## Response Language Rule
- Create file .md located on `/docs/basic`. Then add new file path to vitepress config: `.vitepress/config.ts`
- **Always respond in Vietnamese (tiếng Việt).**
- Code syntax, variable names, component selectors, technical identifiers, and framework-specific keywords remain in English.
- All explanations, comments, documentation, and guidance are in Vietnamese.

